Package frc.inputs

Interface DriverHid

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    GameHid
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DriverDoubleJoysticks, DriverGamepad, DriverJoystick, GameController
    public interface DriverHid
    Provides a skeleton for all of the functions that the driver's HID (human interface device, e.g. a joystick or gamepad) must proivde.

    This allows for a very simple ability to switch which controllers are used for controlling the robot, since the inputs are completely separated from the robot's code.
